This is a compendium of '''continuous integration software''' that supports a [[software engineering]] practice, [[continuous integration]],<ref>{{Cite book|title=Continuous Integration: Improving Software Quality and Reducing Risk|last=Integration|first=Continuous|publisher=Pearson Education|year=2007|isbn=9780321630148|location=|pages=|via=}}</ref> in which developers' changes are immediately tested and reported when they are added to the mainline code base. The comparison of various continuous integration tools is done on the basis of [[Computing platform|platform]], [[Software license|license]], [[Software build|builders]] and [[System integration|Integration]] [[Integrated development environment|IDEs]].

